  "description": "## Bug Report\n\nPlease answer these questions before submitting your issue. Thanks!\n\n### 1. Minimal reproduce step (Required)\nIn my local v8.5.0 environment, it cannot always be reproduced and may require multiple attempts, including creating new sessions.  \nAt the same time, this case can sometimes also be reproduced in the v8.5.2 environment.\n```\nuse test;\nDROP DATABASE IF EXISTS case_1749288575518;\nCREATE DATABASE case_1749288575518;\nUSE case_1749288575518;\nCREATE TABLE t0(c0 INT DEFAULT 1258793663 , PRIMARY KEY(c0));\nALTER TABLE t0 SET TIFLASH REPLICA 1;\nALTER TABLE t0 ADD COLUMN dyn_col_1749288575518 BIGINT DEFAULT 397764731;\nCREATE INDEX idx_1749288577718 ON t0 (dyn_col_1749288575518);\nINSERT IGNORE INTO t0 (dyn_col_1749288575518, c0) VALUES (-8404569, 264315637);\nALTER TABLE t0 MODIFY COLUMN dyn_col_1749288575518 DOUBLE;\nINSERT IGNORE INTO t0 (c0) VALUES (1618048633);\n\nSELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tikv[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\nSELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tiflash[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\n```\n<!-- a step by step guide for reproducing the bug. -->\n\n### 2. What did you expect to see? (Required)\nThe same query returns the same results on both TiKV and TiFlash.\n### 3. What did you see instead (Required)\n```\nmysql> SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tikv[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\n+------------+-----------------------+\n| c0         | dyn_col_1749288575518 |\n+------------+-----------------------+\n| 1618048633 |                  NULL |\n|  264315637 |              -8404569 |\n+------------+-----------------------+\n2 rows in set (0.00 sec)\n\nmysql> SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tiflash[t0]) */ * FROM t0;\n+------------+-----------------------+\n| c0         | dyn_col_1749288575518 |\n+------------+-----------------------+\n|  264315637 |              -8404569 |\n| 1618048633 |             397764731 |\n+------------+-----------------------+\n2 rows in set (0.00 sec)\n```\nexplain info\n```\nmysql> explain SELECT /*+ read_from_storage(tikv[t0]) 